text.english: He will choose our inheritance for us, The excellence of Jacob whom He loves.Selah God has gone up with a shout, The LORD with the sound of a trumpet.
text.arabic: يَخْتَارُ لَنَا نَصِيبَنَا فَخْرَ يَعْقُوبَ الَّذِي أَحَبَّهُ. سِلاَهْ. صَعِدَ اللهُ بِهُتَافٍ الرَّبُّ بِصَوْتِ الصُّورِ.
